metadata.name: Circular Cluster_Colors #1
metadata.description:
This work began with interest in Christian philosophy. However, the concept of her work is not emotional one but based on the fundamental principle of quantum mechanics. Her most recent series of work “Circular Cluster” show circles in the form of atoms re-invigorating in colors as soon as they receive light.
